 Children Privacy\n\n

 These Services do not address anyone under the age of 18. I do not knowingly collect personally identifiable information
  from children under 18. In the case I discover that a child under 18 has provided me with personal information,
  I immediately delete this from our servers. If you are a parent or guardian and you are aware that your child has
  provided us with personal information, please contact me so that I will be able to do necessary actions.\n\n

